{"tid":526872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HKExpress 推男體盛廣告 歧視男性？","createTime":"2018-01-12T05:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T13:23:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f19d5dbb9e2124629dabe44a22180680ca6c5ae2","tid":526872,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKExpress/videos/745290812336268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKExpress%2Fvideos%2F745290812336268%2F&d=q8Q%2FikaDq42l84lzVNhS%2BU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b30317d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKExpress/videos/745290812336268/</a><br />\n<br />\n【有食唔食罪大惡極】贏取雙人來回機票*<br />\n不論男女，個個都鍾意食正嘢㗎啦，但唔通樣樣嘢都敢食咩？人一世物一世，唔食盡世界又點對得住自己呀！不如試下好似片中主角咁，勇於嘗試人體盛，先係非一般嘅旅遊！依家就睇片估下男模身上壽司嘅總重量，即有機會贏走東京免費雙人來回機票，到時您想點食就點食啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n小貼士：<br />\n最輕係北寄貝壽司得 24g；<br />\n最重係花之戀壽司有 46g<br />\n <br />\n遊戲詳情：<br />\n1. 留言估下片中男模身上壽司嘅總重量，答得最快、最準確嘅 3 位朋友，即有機會贏得東京雙人來回機票<br />\n2. 截止日期為 2018 年 1 月 14 日中午 12 時"},{"pid":"2dfb276d220b1d8a5c227f5e3eab90533e9ef93b","tid":526872,"uid":122,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"掉換既話又會話貶低女人"},{"pid":"7a35d602dae4bdeb12db9cc7fc8338f78f613a95","tid":526872,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb276d220b1d8a5c227f5e3eab90533e9ef93b","tid":526872,"uid":122,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"掉換既話又會話貶低女人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314f7d4cfe2eea01a3b9da1dd4638be51c1e47fd","tid":526872,"uid":531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"試下過幾星期做一次女體盛廣告，睇下有冇人嘈"},{"pid":"639498505abaa305fe95172459e77223f8713462","tid":526872,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05: